casebody.data:
Jeffrey Scott BARBOUR
v.
STATE of North Carolina. No. 417P03-2. Supreme Court of North Carolina. January 26, 2006. Jeffrey Scott Barbour, Pro Se. William P. Hart, Senior Deputy Attorney General, Michael Parker, District Attorney, for State.

ORDER

Upon consideration of the petition filed by Respondent on the 3rd day of January 2006 in this matter for a writ of certiorari to review the order of the Superior Court, Richmond County, the following order was entered and is hereby certified to the Superior Court of that County:

"Dismissed by order of the Court in conference, this the 26th day of January 2006."
